**Summary:** Amplitude's Anomaly + Forecast feature uses Prophet-based algorithms to detect statistically significant deviations in time-series data across Event Segmentation, Conversion over Time, User Sessions, Retention over Time, and Stickiness over Time charts, offering agile/robust/custom modes with configurable confidence intervals and training data durations (120-365 days default).

